title: Do The General Public Know Who KSI Is? | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh hits the streets to find out if the general public knows who popular YouTuber KSI is.
summary: Max Fosh conducts interviews with random people to see if they are aware of KSI's fame and popularity.
payoff: The humor comes from the various reactions and responses of people who either recognize KSI immediately or have no idea who he is, showcasing the varying levels of awareness of internet celebrities among the general public.
